                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Le Bœuf superbe qui laboure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Ou l'Âne, heureux d'avoir marché,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Qui, sur son dos, porte au marché,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Des légumes, et que l'on bourre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Va chercher une entrave ailleurs !\nImite les bons travailleurs :\nLe Bœuf superbe qui laboure,\nOu l'Âne, heureux d'avoir marché,\nQui, sur son dos, porte au marché,\nDes légumes, et que l'on bourre."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Et nous-mêmes, sans nous vanter,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Vois, nous ne savons qu'inventer",
